地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=d3c26f50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"c0b07dbc648f509f21b3add6e1e2f0f3761ed4f7","tid":2032542,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"我出街好守法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68d53b1d5f20d4e50ecd02e7cc0eade49dd9515","tid":2032542,"uid":134744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"各區就唔好喇<br />\n香港九龍各一個就得<br />\n太散姐係同自殺無分別"},{"pid":"fb013f34628c7113230e17de10b2e5ed3e17d4bb","tid":2032542,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da306d2e75fc8e8f196b4007e40476409934eeff","tid":2032542,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"係一定要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"我良好市民黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005065b3481a9e9aacb5a31545898623fadd930e","tid":2032542,"uid":272013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl